{"title":"锣鼓声中","authors":["李学鳌"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣鼓声中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"541工厂工人  李学鳌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老记者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老记者，真叫棒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能写稿，能照像。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写的文章呱呱叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照的像片似活样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天到工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"专把“跃进”来采访。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一车间跃进的最好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二车间的成绩最强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三车间已获“优胜旗”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四车间已登“英雄榜”。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这边，锣声未落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那边，鼓声又响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选哪些镜头？选哪些镜头？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老练的记者啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在路口，没了主张！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报喜队"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咚嘣呛！咚嘣呛！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千人跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万人唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢欢乐乐在路上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳得“蓝箭”入了地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳得“红箭”射天上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕红箭代表生产率，蓝箭代表废品率。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}